description: This Chainlink VRF common Cooter purrs with a rating of 52, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 104, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Box for East, Leverage for South, and 1 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90522-34612-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [104 Votes, Common]
